result.adr_address: 9 Nam Ning St, Aberdeen, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 9 Nam Ning St, Aberdeen, Hong Kong
result.name: Best Hotpot Restaurant

reviews.text: It is a well-known restaurant located in Aberdeen. It offers Chinese food, dim sum and hot pot. Once, my friends and I came here for dinner. We ordered some dishes including a deep sea grouper. The chef cooked it in two ways, one was steamed and the other was fried. very delicious. This restaurant is famous for its hot pot. That night, I saw a lot of people eating hot pot. This proves that the quality is good. Washroom is not acceptable. It is wet, dirty and no one cleans up.
This restaurant serves one of the best dim sum in HK.
Tidy little restaurant good for morning tea.
Nice food
Not the best hot pot in town.

result.name: 百味王火鍋酒家

reviews.text: It is a well-known restaurant located in Aberdeen. It offers Chinese food, dim sum and hot pot. Once, my friends and I came here for dinner. We ordered some dishes including a deep sea grouper. The chef cooked it in two ways, one was steamed and the other was fried. very delicious. This restaurant is famous for its hot pot. That night, I saw a lot of people eating hot pot. This proves that the quality is good. Washroom is not acceptable. It is wet, dirty and no one cleans up.
This restaurant serves one of the best dim sum in HK.
点心夠熱夠新鲜，味道一流，份量充足，價錢合理偏抵吃。環境舒適。不過可能要被搭抬。但洗手間環境有待改善！
食物新鲜，美味！份量十足，尤以火煱更为出色。地方不算大，但是环境清诘。员工服务态度誠懇、有礼貌，特别是其总管梁先生！
